History Of Jazz - Lecture 30 By Dave Jasen (Professor, C W Post, L.I .N.Y.) On "Red Nichols", Using His Recordings. Copyright Information Below. David A. Jasen produced this video in the 1970's for C.W. Post College located in Long Island, New York. He used his own Original Records that he owns of the tunes in this video. You can buy some performer’s and Dave's albums and CD'S on Amazon.com or Google Dave Jasen. This video is for educational purposes only. It is covered under "Fair Use".
